title: Afro-Cuban All Stars - 5 Albums (1997 - 2005)
description:
Lead by ex-Sierra Maestra drummer Juan De Marcos Gonzalez, the Afro-Cuban All Stars have been essential to the growing worldwide popularity of Afro-Cuban music.
